    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Official Statistics
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Results from Phases 1 to 4 of the NISRA Coronavirus (COVID-19) Opinion Survey
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Results from phases 1 to 4 of the NISRA Coronavirus (COVID-19) Opinion Survey. The survey is designed to measure how the COVID-19 pandemic is affecting peoples’ lives and behaviour in Northern Ireland. The results relate to phases 1, 2, 3 and 4 of the survey and are based on interviews carried out with members of the public between 21 April and 17 September 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

