    <h2 class="title"><a rel="external" href="https://www.nisra.gov.uk/publications/nisra-coronavirus-covid-19-opinion-survey">Results from Phases 1 to 4 of the NISRA Coronavirus (COVID-19) Opinion Survey</a></h2>
