      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>On 20 April 2020, NISRA launched a new NISRA Coronavirus (COVID-19) Opinion Survey designed to measure how the COVID-19 pandemic was affecting peoples’ lives and behaviour in Northern Ireland.</p>

<p>This publication summarises the key findings from Phases 1 to 4 of the NISRA COVID-19 Opinion survey and is based on interviews carried out with members of the public between 21 April and 17 September 2020.</p>

<p>NISRA is currently planning to carry out seven phases of the survey.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

